{"tid":1725954,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"正式宣佈依家割席","createTime":"2019-11-16T02:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:06:52.000Z","uid":317282,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d29febe306a3c565f7ae2bc6dca7597e3530016f","tid":1725954,"uid":317282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"係人都知道 <span style=\"color: red;\">黃係就連選舉延遲都唔想</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府同建制派係好驚 <span style=\"color: blue;\">佢哋係好想取消選舉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府其實好聰明 派建制派出嚟講話想要延遲選舉<br />\n但自己就一路話絕對唔會延遲 要將區議會選舉全力推行<br />\n完美咁將自己嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">奸計</span>掩飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選舉當日 除咗投票之外我哋唔會有任何行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然而<span style=\"color: red;\">對家一定會有人搞事</span> 例如元朗721當日有唔少廢青 只要佢哋換咗件黑色衫然後破壞選舉 政府一定會入晒我哋數<br />\n你可能會話 入我哋數都無所謂 反正其實我哋嗰邊都知道呢啲喺選舉日搞事嘅人一定係對家嘅人<br />\n但係有冇諗過 <span style=\"color: gold;\">國際未必咁諗 就連班香港既遊離派都未必會咁諗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉日出事 政府同建制派一定會屈我哋再炒大來講</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n務求將民意 包括國際社會嘅聲音完全逆轉<br />\n<br />\n正如我所講 我地呢邊係要選舉順利進行<br />\n為咗唔俾建制派同政府搞事得逞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所有以任何方式影響選舉進行嘅都唔會係同路人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋必須而家割席</span></span><br />\n冇錯 係而家 正所謂<span style=\"color: red;\">先下手為強</span><br />\n我哋要<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做大文宣</span></span><br />\n將<span style=\"color: gold;\">「選舉日搞事嘅人唔係同路人」</span>呢個概念變成新嘅社<span style=\"color: pink;\">會共識</span> 就好似五大訴求一樣<br />\nfb ig 仲有街上面嘅實體海報都要做文宣<br />\n做到街知巷聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再將<span style=\"color: purple;\">「建制派好唔希望進行選舉 以免結果對自己不利」</span>呢種想法傳揚開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要全香港都知道 我哋係最希望民意能夠傳到入議會入邊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">相反政府同埋建制派係最唔希望聽到任何民意</span><br />\n<br />\n宣布割席係非常極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係留意番 <span style=\"color: orange;\">割既只不過響選舉日搞事嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我哋都知道嗰啲亦都只不過係對家嘅人</span><br />\n我哋唔會傷害到我哋嘅勇武<br />\n而且割席正正因為佢咁極端 先至能夠引起到廣泛嘅注意<br />\n<br />\n我知道呢幾日大家都好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係咁多位和理非諗諗<br />\n勇武為咗爭取民主自由以及人權公義 佢哋喺度幫緊我哋擋子彈啊仆你個臭街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地和理非<span style=\"color: red;\">就算攰都一定要行落去</span><br />\n為咗選舉順利進行 為咗我哋嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.S. P牌仔一個推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位巴絲如果認同我所講嘅嘢嘅話唔該你地幫我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"45fd43df981e15d87d402a4e1049d4d48b03b1bc","tid":1725954,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"區選取消其實先最有利迫使歐美做野，想區選如期只有政客"},{"pid":"d663b969fa0af0b0cec20ca840604b92382477af","tid":1725954,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"On9 吹休息風 選贏左做議員份糧出比我夠<br />\n阿？"}]}